<abstract><t>This document specifies a change to the IETF process in which Internet Drafts and RFCs are allowed to contain non-ASCII characters. The proposed change is to change the encoding of Internet Drafts and RFCs to UTF-8 when non-ASCII characters are needed.</t></abstract>

